"A.P.238/4/8": "...Speaking of, that Huey was planning some kind of tournament. I heard that it's coming up soon."
"...You have to form a party to participate. It's assessing our ability to fight as a team."
"...We'll have to co-operate to take on many more powerful enemies from now on, so that makes sense."
"...If you haven't decided yet, would you like to join me?"
"...Not that you have to decide now. On the day, just give me a call."
